## Limitations
The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full spectrum of opinions and research on the topic. Additionally, the reliance on online platforms like Reddit and Quora may introduce bias, as these are user-generated content sites. Further research, including academic studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.